'''Paul Rice''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed the [[Jeby]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the under 16 years old category. He was 7 at the time his entry was published.

The planet [[Rainboh]], which Rice created for his backstory for the Jeby, was [[canon]]ized with its placement in the [[Hapes Cluster/Legends|Hapes Cluster]] in ''[[The Essential Atlas]]''.

